ActCanadian International Trade Tribunal Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian International Trade Tribunal Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL REGULATIONS in order to implement Canada's rights and obligations relating to the bilateral emergency action provisions under the Canada-EFTA Free Trade Agreement (CEFTA) and the Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA).
